Class InvalidDataConversionException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class InvalidDataConversionException
extends FormattedRuntimeException
    General invalid conversion exception.

    Exception that gets thrown if you try to perform an invalid conversion, such as when calling ObjectMap.getInt(...) on a non-numeric String.
